original_title: An Officer and A Gentleman: Mark Haskins and Travis Banks
overview: Hey YO Adrian! It's time to get weird on this special episode of An Officer and A Gentleman with two guests Travis Banks and Mark Haskins. If your into weird ghost stories, Predator, and sky cranking you are going to love this. Get ready to hear the greatest review of Jurassic Park ever and enjoy all the usual wackiness. Special appearances by Ricochet and Trevor Lee add to the craziness as you get all the scoops on how these lads poop and pee.
title: An Officer and A Gentleman: Mark Haskins and Travis Banks
